---
import CaseStudyLayout from "../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro";

const meta = [
  { label: "Year", value: "2021" },
  { label: "Client", value: "Gener8" },
];

const stats = [
  { value: "200k+", label: "Downloads" },
  { value: "120k", label: "Daily users" },
  { value: "7mo", label: "To Dragons' Den" },
  { value: "1", label: "Sole designer" },
];
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  pageTitle="Gener8 - Sammy Norris"
  meta={meta}
  description="A first-of-its-kind browser extension that lets users profit from the ads they see. I was brought in as the sole designer to turn a genuinely novel proposition into something simple enough to download and trust."
  signoff="Designed at Gener8"
  signoffYear="2021"
  nextProject={{ title: "Larkbury", slug: "larkbury" }}
  heroIntro
>
  <Fragment slot="title">Gener<em>8</em></Fragment>

  <!-- Figure 01 - hero shot -->
  <figure class="figure is-loose is-bind-top" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-1-m.webp" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-1-m.jpg" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-1.webp" width="2400" height="1800" />
      <img src="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-1.jpg" alt="Gener8 marketing site hero" loading="eager" decoding="async" width="2400" height="1800" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Chapter I - Challenge -->
  <section class="chapter is-tight" data-reveal>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num" aria-hidden="true">I.</span>
      <h2 class="chapter__label b2">The challenge</h2>
    </header>

    <blockquote class="chapter__quote">
      A genuinely novel product entering a crowded and sceptical market - 
      where the design challenge was as much about trust and clarity as it
      was about aesthetics.
    </blockquote>

    <div class="chapter__body">
      <p class="b1">
        Gener8 flips the advertising model: instead of passively serving ads, it lets users opt in, earn from the ads they see, and take back control of their data. The product was real. The challenge was making it feel credible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Figure 02 -->
  <figure class="figure is-loose" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-2-m.webp" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-2-m.jpg" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-2.webp" width="2400" height="1800" />
      <img src="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-2.jpg" alt="Gener8 marketing site sections" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2400" height="1800" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Chapter II - Process -->
  <section class="chapter is-tight" data-reveal>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num" aria-hidden="true">II.</span>
      <h2 class="chapter__label b2">The process</h2>
    </header>

    <h3 class="chapter__h2">
      One designer, one CEO, <em>three months.</em>
    </h3>

    <div class="chapter__body chapter__body--double">
      <p class="b1">
        Working directly with the CEO over three months, I delivered the full design across the marketing website, browser extension UI, and companion app. My work covered wireframes and user flows, copy direction to make an unfamiliar proposition feel simple and trustworthy, a CRO-led website structure designed to turn curiosity into downloads, and extension and app UI from low fidelity through to final assets.
      </p>
      <p class="b1">
        The design had one job: explain what Gener8 was, why it was different, and why users could trust it - without overwhelming them. Every decision traced back to that.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Figure 03 -->
  <figure class="figure is-loose-max" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-3-m.webp" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-3-m.jpg" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-3.webp" width="2400" height="1800" />
      <img src="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-3.jpg" alt="Extension UI details" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2400" height="1800" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Chapter III - Outcome -->
  <section class="chapter" data-reveal>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num" aria-hidden="true">III.</span>
      <h2 class="chapter__label b2">The outcome</h2>
    </header>

    <blockquote class="chapter__quote">
      The site generated over 200,000 user downloads, and seven months after
      launch Gener8 secured investment on Dragons' Den. The product now has
      over 120,000 daily active users.
    </blockquote>

    <div class="stats">
      {stats.map((s) => (
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__value">{s.value}</span>
          <span class="stat__label b3">{s.label}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Figure 04 -->
  <figure class="figure" data-reveal>
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-4-m.webp" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-4-m.jpg" width="2250" height="3000" />
      <source type="image/webp" srcset="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-4.webp" width="2400" height="1800" />
      <img src="/images/projects/gener8/image-gener8-4.jpg" alt="Gener8 product screens" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2400" height="1800" />
    </picture>
  </figure>

  <!-- Figure 05 - YouTube video -->
  <figure class="figure figure--video" data-reveal>
    <div class="video-frame">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/dfUfwg1pY2s?rel=0"
        title="Gener8 product video"
        loading="lazy"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </figure>
</CaseStudyLayout>

<style is:global>
  /* Video figure - same card-frame as images */
  .figure--video .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 8px;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
  }
  .figure--video iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 8px;
    width: calc(100% - 16px);
    height: calc(100% - 16px);
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 18px;
  }
</style>
